It's dangerous!

162
00:14:54,727 --> 00:14:56,186
My goodness! Oh, no!

163
00:14:56,353 --> 00:14:57,855
It's dangerous!

164
00:14:59,231 --> 00:15:01,191
-I said it's dangerous!
-What should we do?

165
00:15:02,026 --> 00:15:03,110
What should we do?

166
00:15:04,904 --> 00:15:06,906
My goodness, come down!

167
00:15:07,615 --> 00:15:09,533
-Please come down!
-It's dangerous!

168
00:15:09,783 --> 00:15:11,744
It's a piece of cake for me.

169
00:15:12,870 --> 00:15:14,413
I've practiced it over 1,000 times.

170
00:15:14,705 --> 00:15:15,831
I can do it with my eyes closed.

171
