174
00:15:33,349 --> 00:15:34,308
Mom.

175
00:15:35,392 --> 00:15:36,352
Dad.

176
00:15:36,936 --> 00:15:38,896
I can't see a thing.

177
00:15:54,411 --> 00:15:56,705
They say that a ballerina dies twice.

178
00:15:57,498 --> 00:15:59,416
The first time is when we give up ballet.

179
00:16:00,501 --> 00:16:02,378
The second time is when we stop breathing.

180
00:16:03,212 --> 00:16:04,672
When I stopped being a dancer,

181
00:16:04,922 --> 00:16:06,340
