There's no way she heard me.

201
00:18:51,088 --> 00:18:52,256
You were a guy?

202
00:18:54,925 --> 00:18:55,968
What?

203
00:18:56,218 --> 00:18:58,137
Can you hear me? You can?

204
00:18:58,220 --> 00:19:00,347
I told you clearly
that my hearing is just fine.

205
00:19:01,849 --> 00:19:03,058
How could this be possible?

206
00:19:03,142 --> 00:19:04,351
I should be asking that.

207
00:19:04,685 --> 00:19:06,353
How could this happen twice in one day?

208
00:19:07,729 --> 00:19:09,940
What's your deal? Pickpocket? Pervert?

209
00:19:10,357 --> 00:19:11,859
What is it that you're after?

210
00:19:12,067 --> 00:19:15,404
I doubt that you sat next to a blind woman
just to watch the rain.

211
00:19:15,612 --> 00:19:16,738
Wait.

212
00:19:16,905 --> 00:19:17,823
Forget it.

213
00:19:18,407 --> 00:19:19,950
I caught you, so just leave.

214
00:19:20,117 --> 00:19:21,827
If you keep bothering me, you'll get hurt.

215
00:19:23,662 --> 00:19:24,496
Wait

216
00:19:25,747 --> 00:19:26,832
I don't want to!

217
00:19:27,875 --> 00:19:28,876
What?

218
00:19:32,087 --> 00:19:34,214
This bench does not belong to you or me.

219
00:19:34,298 --> 00:19:36,633
