223
00:19:44,808 --> 00:19:45,893
How dare you?

224
00:19:46,059 --> 00:19:47,644
You have such a foul mouth.

225
00:19:47,936 --> 00:19:48,812
Listen.

226
00:19:49,021 --> 00:19:51,190
Whatever binds you here
will continue to bind you up above.

227
00:19:51,273 --> 00:19:52,441
-And--
-I don't need that.

228
00:19:53,650 --> 00:19:55,110
Be it Buddha, Jesus, or Allah.

229
00:19:55,360 --> 00:19:56,445
I won't believe anyone.

230
00:19:58,488 --> 00:20:01,116
Those who deny
the deity's existence will face--

231
00:20:01,200 --> 00:20:02,451
I didn't say that.

232
00:20:02,534 --> 00:20:04,244
A deity? Of course, there's a deity.

233
00:20:04,328 --> 00:20:06,538
It's just that the deity is a jerk.

234
00:20:07,664 --> 00:20:09,041
"A jerk"?

235
00:20:11,418 --> 00:20:12,377
Those who blaspheme

236
00:20:12,461 --> 00:20:14,046
-against the deity--
-He won't listen to me

237
00:20:14,129 --> 00:20:15,255
no matter how hard I pray.

238
00:20:15,714 --> 00:20:17,925
He ignores my wish when it's my only wish.

239
00:20:18,634 --> 00:20:20,969
I asked Him to keep my dad
alive for one more day

240
00:20:21,136 --> 00:20:23,513
to let me see my dad for
a week before he died.

241
00:20:24,473 --> 00:20:26,099
I cried and prayed for
11 hours on the plane,

242
00:20:26,183 --> 00:20:27,226
but He didn't listen.

243
00:20:27,601 --> 00:20:28,685
I asked Him

244
00:20:29,311 --> 00:20:30,854
to take one of my limbs
instead of my eyes.

245
00:20:31,396 --> 00:20:32,689
That way, I could still be a dancer.

246
00:20:32,773 --> 00:20:34,316
But he still ignored me.

247
00:20:36,193 --> 00:20:38,445
That's what the deity,
your one and only, did to me.

248
00:20:40,155 --> 00:20:41,573
Not everyone behaves like you

249
00:20:41,740 --> 00:20:43,492
after experiencing a tragedy.

250
00:20:45,285 --> 00:20:47,621
Not everyone jumps off
the bridge like you.

251
00:20:52,000 --> 00:20:53,085
Who are you?

252
00:20:56,255 --> 00:20:57,506
-She can grab me?
-You.

253
00:20:57,756 --> 00:20:58,966
Who are you?

