To be precise,
the 20th anniversary is next week.

274
00:22:17,836 --> 00:22:19,212
Is Yeon-seo coming?

275
00:22:19,338 --> 00:22:20,255
Ms. Choi.

276
00:22:20,339 --> 00:22:22,174
