304
00:23:30,492 --> 00:23:32,244
regarding the canceled donation this time.

305
00:23:36,665 --> 00:23:37,833
Don't make a fuss.

306
00:23:37,916 --> 00:23:39,835
-The transplant list--
-Of course.

307
00:23:40,669 --> 00:23:42,587
No one would try to hinder
the donation process.

308
00:23:43,380 --> 00:23:44,714
If someone did,

309
