So are you telling me that you told him

317
00:24:38,435 --> 00:24:39,436
the truth?

318
00:24:39,811 --> 00:24:41,730
Today, I pretended that
I didn't know anything.

319
00:24:41,813 --> 00:24:43,940
-"Today"?
-I can't do this anymore.

320
00:24:44,357 --> 00:24:45,567
I'm a doctor too.

321
00:24:45,942 --> 00:24:47,819
