and everything else.

329
00:25:09,674 --> 00:25:11,176
If there's an investigation...

330
00:25:12,594 --> 00:25:13,595
No.

331
00:25:13,970 --> 00:25:15,305
That won't happen.

332
00:25:15,972 --> 00:25:17,515
No, that can't happen.

333
00:25:18,350 --> 00:25:19,351
Investigation?

334
00:25:20,018 --> 00:25:21,603
Just keep this in mind.

335
00:25:21,686 --> 00:25:23,396
Dr. Kim, you crossed a bridge.

336
00:25:23,939 --> 00:25:26,775
And I destroyed that bridge.

337
