My dear client, are you alive?

348
00:27:13,715 --> 00:27:14,966
What will happen to that cat?

349
00:27:16,134 --> 00:27:18,386
I'm sorry, cat. I didn't see you there.

350
00:27:18,845 --> 00:27:21,306
