so they will take good care of it.

351
00:27:22,432 --> 00:27:23,558
Stop crying and drink some tea.

352
00:27:23,641 --> 00:27:25,101
If you cry, you'll run out of breath.

353
00:27:25,643 --> 00:27:27,437
Ru-na, let's go back.

354
00:27:27,645 --> 00:27:29,939
