and stop crying.

358
00:27:44,120 --> 00:27:45,538
It was just an accident.

359
00:27:45,955 --> 00:27:47,290
You didn't kill it.

360
00:27:47,791 --> 00:27:48,917
But still...

361
00:27:49,125 --> 00:27:51,211
Something tragic just happened to it.

362
00:27:51,586 --> 00:27:53,463
That's what tragedy is like for everyone.

363
00:27:53,755 --> 00:27:56,299
It suddenly comes and takes everything.

364
00:27:57,801 --> 00:27:59,552
You have to get rid of it
before it does that.

365
00:28:00,720 --> 00:28:02,680
So pull yourself together
and stay grounded.

366
00:28:02,764 --> 00:28:04,057
Tomorrow is your performance.

367
00:28:04,474 --> 00:28:06,017
You can't let your heart
and body be shaken.

368
00:28:06,476 --> 00:28:07,394
Ru-na.

369
00:28:09,521 --> 00:28:10,605
So you should

370
00:28:11,981 --> 00:28:14,317
drink this and sleep it off,

371
00:28:14,901 --> 00:28:16,194
Odette.

372
00:28:26,454 --> 00:28:28,039
Goodness.

373
00:28:31,126 --> 00:28:32,001
Goodness.

