Look at you.

375
00:28:34,921 --> 00:28:37,424
Isn't it amazing? The cuteness of babies.

376
00:28:37,841 --> 00:28:40,176
They are much better than humans.

377
00:28:43,805 --> 00:28:46,391
You little rascal. What will you do now?

378
00:28:49,602 --> 00:28:50,770
I'm sorry.

379
00:28:55,024 --> 00:28:56,443
But they're adorable.

380
00:28:56,693 --> 00:28:58,820
Your eyes were filled with love just now.

381
00:28:58,903 --> 00:29:00,447
