382
00:29:00,530 --> 00:29:02,115
You told me to look after
widows and orphans.

383
00:29:02,657 --> 00:29:03,658
An angel's nature

384
00:29:03,742 --> 00:29:05,326
is to love goodness and hate wickedness.

385
00:29:06,244 --> 00:29:07,370
I just

386
00:29:08,496 --> 00:29:09,873
followed my instinct.

387
00:29:10,665 --> 00:29:12,792
I see. That's why you did this.

388
00:29:13,042 --> 00:29:16,254
That's why you pushed a 17-year-old
boy into a shit hole.

389
00:29:16,963 --> 00:29:19,716
"Pushed"? I never touch human beings.

390
00:29:20,008 --> 00:29:22,260
And for your information,
he bullied his childhood friend.

391
