You do have money. It's right here.

392
00:29:24,220 --> 00:29:25,180
That's not all.

393
00:29:25,472 --> 00:29:27,474
You opened the cages full of dogs
that was on the truck

394
00:29:27,557 --> 00:29:29,267
and filled the streets with them.

395
