The deity's great purpose
won't be tampered

400
00:29:40,904 --> 00:29:43,364
with just because a lowly angel
like me flicked a finger. And...

401
00:29:44,741 --> 00:29:46,201
I will be

402
00:29:47,160 --> 00:29:48,661
up there tomorrow anyway.

403
00:29:49,204 --> 00:29:50,205
My term is...

404
00:29:51,998 --> 00:29:54,584
-over.
-You're so annoying.

405
00:29:58,838 --> 00:29:59,881
Hey, Hu.

406
00:30:00,590 --> 00:30:03,593
Humans can't see us, can they?

407
00:30:03,802 --> 00:30:05,845
No matter how spiritual they are.

408
00:30:06,638 --> 00:30:07,555
Who are you?

409
00:30:07,639 --> 00:30:09,641
Why did you sit on this
bench without asking me?

410
00:30:11,601 --> 00:30:13,186
Never mind. I met a sensitive human

411
00:30:13,269 --> 00:30:14,979
who has a very foul mouth today.

412
00:30:15,146 --> 00:30:16,105
You.

413
00:30:16,731 --> 00:30:17,857
Wait, did you...

