If you lay a finger on a human,

417
00:30:27,116 --> 00:30:28,743
you will disappear immediately.

418
00:30:29,911 --> 00:30:32,914
You will disappear like smoke

419
00:30:34,290 --> 00:30:35,208
and dust,

420
00:30:36,668 --> 00:30:37,669
at once.

