00:30:39,337 --> 00:30:40,880
I only have 24 hours left.

422
00:30:40,964 --> 00:30:41,965
Nothing will happen.

423
00:30:42,757 --> 00:30:45,677
I'm anxious because you have
24 hours left.

424
00:30:45,760 --> 00:30:47,720
I feel like you are capable of

425
