a wild and violent human.

428
00:30:55,770 --> 00:30:58,022
My darned sixth sense is heightened
more than ever.

429
00:30:58,106 --> 00:30:58,982
I don't need that.

430
00:30:59,190 --> 00:31:00,567
A deity? Of course, there's a deity.

431
00:31:00,984 --> 00:31:02,735
