448
00:31:58,833 --> 00:32:01,044
Come out, you coward.

449
00:32:01,336 --> 00:32:02,962
You phony...

450
00:32:03,671 --> 00:32:05,006
religious jerk!

451
00:32:08,301 --> 00:32:09,844
