00:33:52,071 --> 00:33:53,156
It's all right.

477
00:33:53,239 --> 00:33:54,615
He's our new secretary.

478
00:33:55,450 --> 00:33:56,701
Hello, Princess.

479
00:33:57,285 --> 00:33:58,703
My name is Cho Seung-hwan.

480
00:33:59,245 --> 00:34:00,580
I hope we can get along.

481
00:34:01,998 --> 00:34:03,624
-Yeon-seo.
-Mr. Cho!

482
00:34:05,251 --> 00:34:06,294
Gosh.

483
00:34:06,502 --> 00:34:07,503
How did I do?

484
00:34:08,212 --> 00:34:09,172
You were the best.

485
00:34:09,255 --> 00:34:12,050
